On Android I can only edit the first lines of a TextField that is embedded inside a NestedScrollView. Lines further down are scrolled out of sight when I try to edit them.
* Not tested on iOS or web.
* Tested on Android emulator and real hardware.

## Steps to Reproduce

<!-- You must include full steps to reproduce so that we can reproduce the problem. -->

1. Run `flutter create bug`.
2. Update the files as follows: 
main.dart:
```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

