Hello, guys!

The `floatingLabelBehavior` attribute is only to set the visibility of the floating label. So, it hasn't  influence on `prefixText` attribute. However, it's possible to generate the expected result whether the `labelText` and `prefixText` attributes are defined with equal value and `floatingLabelBehavior` is setted to `FloatingLabelBehavior.never`.

That will show the labelText when the TextFormField has no focus and will show the prefixText when there's focus.
As they are in same position, the effect is equal to always show the prefix text.

Example code:

```dart
final prefixValue = 'Example: ';

return TextField(
    decoration: InputDecoration(
        floatingLabelBehavior: FloatingLabelBehavior.never,
        prefixText: prefixValue,
        labelText: prefixValue,
    ),
);
```

